                    "description": "Peter de Ruiter\nPwC Africa Tax Partner \n\nFrom 2013 to 2017 Peter was based in Lagos, Nigeria where he worked with his PwC teams of experts as Tax Advisor for the major inbound international investors and for local clients.\n\nNigeria and the West African region are emerging fast and develop into important investment markets for PwC's clients. The economic and business opportunities are immense but coincide with challenging questions about local rules, regulations and business practices. \n\nPwC Nigeria is the firm of choice to answer those questions and to work with our clients to seize the Nigerian and wider African opportunities in the most efficient and practical way.\n\nPeter personally provided advice and assistance to major inbound investors. \n\nHis major fields of industry expertise are in Financial Services, Energy, Real Estate, IT/Telcom.\n \nHis Tax Specialty Areas are in International Tax, Financial Structuring, Mergers and Acquisitions, Transfer Pricing, Tax Accounting and Supply Chain.\n \nPeter has a Master Degree in Fiscal Law, graduated at The Leiden University, The Netherlands. He is a member of the Dutch Bar of Tax Advisors.\n \nHe is fluent in Dutch, English, German and French.",
